trans-unit.source: Represents an event that an instance store raises to notify hosts about a condition.
trans-unit.target: Representa um evento que um repositório de instâncias gera para notificar os hosts sobre uma condição.

trans-unit.source: Examples: <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasRunnableWorkflowEvent" /> and <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasActivatableWorkflowEvent" />.
trans-unit.target: Exemplos: <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasRunnableWorkflowEvent" /> e <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasActivatableWorkflowEvent" />.

trans-unit.source: Compares two instances of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Compara duas instâncias dos objetos <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" />.

trans-unit.source: The object to be compared with the current object.
trans-unit.target: O objeto a ser comparado ao objeto atual.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the current <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object and the passed object converted as the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> are the same.
trans-unit.target: Determina se o objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> atual e o objeto passado transmitido convertido como o <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> são iguais.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see langword="True" /> if the objects are same; otherwise, returns <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: Retornará <see langword="True" /> se os objetos forem iguais; caso contrário, retornará <see langword="False" />.

trans-unit.source: The object to be compared with the current object.
trans-unit.target: O objeto a ser comparado ao objeto atual.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the current <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object and the passed <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object are the same.
trans-unit.target: Determina se o objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> atual e o objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> transmitido são iguais.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see langword="True" /> if the objects are same; otherwise, returns <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: Retornará <see langword="True" /> se os objetos forem iguais; caso contrário, retornará <see langword="False" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o código hash da instância de <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" />.

trans-unit.source: The hash code for the instance.
trans-unit.target: O código hash para a instância.

trans-unit.source: Returns the XName (namespace combined with name) of the persistence event.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o XName (namespace combinado com o nome) do evento de persistência.

trans-unit.source: XName of the persistence event
trans-unit.target: XName do evento de persistência

trans-unit.source: The first <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> a ser comparado.

trans-unit.source: The second <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: O segundo objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> a ser comparado.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> objects are the same.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um valor que indica se os objetos <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> especificados são iguais.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the two objects are the same; otherwise, <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="True" /> se os dois objetos forem iguais; caso contrário, <see langword="False" />.

trans-unit.source: The first <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> a ser comparado.

trans-unit.target: O segundo objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> a ser comparado.
